# Normalise line endings: store text as LF in the repo, check out native.
* text=auto

# Keep genuinely-binary assets untouched (no EOL or diff munging).
# SVG is intentionally omitted: it is text, and normalising to LF keeps
# favicon.svg byte-identical to the LF copy already committed (the hub asset).
*.png   binary
*.ico   binary
*.parquet binary
